<html lang="en-US">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Shared resources overdue</title>
  </head>

 <body>
Dear <%= @borrower.name %> (<%= @borrower.email %>),

It appears the following shared resources are still being borrowed by you. Please return them and scan them in as Available at your earliest convenience:

<% @assets.each do |asset| %>
  <%= link_to asset.name, asset_url(asset) %>
<% end %>

Thanks,

Your Majordomo
 </body>
</html>
